bug.short_desc: URL bar is not redrawn after tap on Android search button when having Edit Bookmark popup on

assigned_to.name: Nobody; OK to take it and work on it

long_desc.thetext:
Created attachment 524626 Overlap
Mozilla /5.0 (Android;Linux armv7l;rv:2.2a1pre) Gecko/20110407 Firefox/4.2a1pre Fennec /4.1a1pre Device: Samsung Captivate (Android 2.1 update 1)
Steps to reproduce: 1. Go to any website 2. Tap on the Bookmark Star > Edit 3. Click on search button of your Android system
Expected results: Awesomebar should appear with no problem
Actual results: The URL bar is overlapped. Please see the screenshot.
